                Ribbon on the top of the screen, then choose the <b>Translate</b> button and
                finally select <b>Translate Document</b>. A message window will pop-up to let
                you know that this document will be sent to Microsoft Translator on the Web:
            </span>
        </span>
    </p>

    <p class=MsoNormal>
        <span class=apple-converted-space>
            <span style='color:black;
background:white'>
                <img border=0 width=655 height=368 id="Picture 11"
